dcterms:creator: R. Wetzker

C. Bauckhage
dcterms:description: A small toy dataset created with the help of multiple SEAL queries with 'Apple' as a fruit and as a company. It is created to demonstrate the entity disambiguation effect of using triplet records and to compare various clustering algorithms.
dcterms:title: Toy Apple

dcterms:creator: R. Wetzker
C. Zimmermann
C. Bauckhage
dcterms:description: A dataset that is a subset of DAI-Labor Delicious corpus, created by taking only those URLs which are tagged as 'sports'.
dcterms:title: Delicious Sports

dcterms:creator: R. Wetzker
C. Zimmermann
C. Bauckhage
dcterms:description: A dataset that is a subset of DAI-Labor Delicious corpus, created by taking only those URLs which are tagged as 'music'.
dcterms:title: Delicious Music

dcterms:creator: A. Carlson
J. Betteridge
R. C. Wang
E. R. Hruschka, Jr.

dcterms:description: CSEAL is one of the methods which suggest new category and relation instances to NELL KB. CSEAL Useful dataset is a collection of those HTML pages from which CSEAL gathered information about entities in the NELL KB.
dcterms:title: CSEAL Useful

dcterms:creator: R. C. Wang
W. W. Cohen
dcterms:description: This dataset is collected using hypernyms associated with entities in the NELL KB as queries for ASIA. Examples of such hypernyms are 'City', 'Bird', 'Sports team' etc.
dcterms:title: ASIA NELL

dcterms:creator: R. C. Wang
W. W. Cohen
dcterms:description: This dataset is also collected using the ASIA system but with another set of category names as input. These category names come from 'Intelligence domain'.
dcterms:title: ASIA INT

dcterms:creator: J. Callan
dcterms:description: This dataset is collected by randomly sampling high pagerank pages in the Clueweb dataset. It contains a random sample of the Clueweb dataset.
dcterms:title: Clueweb HPR
